| [IGI 3.06ct Fancy Black-CO Pear](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/black-23322623?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | [$4,073](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/black-23322623?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) |
| [IGI 3.07ct Fancy Black-CO Pear](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/black-28319880?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | [$4,086](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/black-28319880?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) |

**On GIA vs. IGI for black diamonds.** Both GIA and IGI certify black diamonds identically — the Fancy Black grade with CO clarity is the same designation from both labs. For transparent colorless and colored diamonds, lab differences matter because saturation and cut grades carry nuance. For opaque black diamonds with a universal color grade and a clarity designation that is optically irrelevant, the certification lab difference is negligible in practice. The [IGI 2.66ct at $3,541](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/black-28319883?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) and the [GIA 2.42ct at $3,547](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/black-29304267?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) at nearly identical prices — the IGI delivers 0.24ct more black pear for the same money. Choose by size and dimensions, not lab name.

The [IGI 3.00ct at $3,993](https://www.bluenile.com/colored-diamond-details/black-28319884?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) is a compelling benchmark: a 3ct black pear for under $4,000. At approximately 11.5mm × 7.5mm face-up, a 3ct black pear is unmistakably bold. Combined with the [Scalloped Pavé](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/scalloped-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-item-sku-192886?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) at [$1,970 (164 reviews)](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/scalloped-pave-diamond-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-item-sku-192886?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational), total ring is approximately $5,963.

