| [Graduated Diamond Halo Engagement Ring in 14k White Gold by James Allen](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/graduated-diamond-halo-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-305177?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | [$2,985](https://www.bluenile.com/engagement-rings/design-your-own-ring/graduated-diamond-halo-engagement-ring-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-305177?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 99 |
