### Yellow Gold Settings: Gothic Romantic

Yellow gold creates an intentional warm-contrast aesthetic with a black pear — the combination reads as gothic-romantic rather than stark modern. Victorian milgrain and scroll elements amplify this aesthetic, referencing memento mori and mourning jewelry traditions where black stones (jet, onyx, black diamonds) were set in gold.

